<!--Eligibility Reqs-->
<section class="bg-gradient-to-b from-blue-50 to-blue-200 text-black py-20">
  <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center justify-center">
    <!--Text-->
    <div class="lg:w-1/2 flex flex-col items-center lg:items-end">
      <!--Container for text to align them-->
      <div class="lg:text-left">
        <h2 class="font-semibold text-2xl lg:text-4xl text-center pb-4">What Are the Eligibility Requirements to Become a CFI?</h2>
        <div class="text-base px-6 lg:pl-0 lg:pr-8">
          <p class="my-2 pb-5 font-semibold text-2xl">
            Requirements:
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside border-b-2 border-slate-300 pb-3 pl-3">
              <li class="mb-2">Must be minimum age of 18.</li>
              <li class="mb-2">Possess a strong command of the English language, ensuring your ability to read, speak, write, and understand effectively.</li>
              <li class="mb-2">
                Hold either a <a class="text-blue-800 hover:underline" href="<%= commercial_certificate_path %>">commercial pilot certificate</a>
                or an airline transport pilot certificate with an <a class="text-blue-800 hover:underline" href="<%= instrument_rating_path %>">instrument rating</a>.
              </li>
              <li class="mb-2">Accumulate a minimum of 250 flight hours
              </li>
              <li class="mb-2">Secure a valid FAA 3rd Class Medical Certificate or a higher class.
              </li>
              <li class="mb-2">Receive a logbook endorsement from an authorized instructor.
              </li>
              <li class="mb-2">Pass a knowledge and practical test to demonstrate your proficiency in aeronautical knowledge areas relevant to the flight instructor rating you're pursuing.
              </li>
            </ul>
          </p>
          <p class="text-xs mt-4">Reference <a class="text-blue-800 hover:underline" href="https://www.ecfr.gov/current/title-14/chapter-I/subchapter-D/part-61#sp14.2.61.h">14 CFR ยง61.183</a> for the entire list of eligibility requirements.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
